Bug modifications that the app crashed on the Mac. iPad version Other minor bug fixes.

Add tag and location filter function. Fixed a bug where the order of tags and locations were mixed up. Fixed a bug where the biometric button was visible in the passcode window. Fixed a bug where Saturday and Sunday colors did not appear in the diary list. Fixed a bug where purchases could not be restored. Fixed a bug with incorrect date notation. Other minor bug fixes. Translation optimization.

The Surprise Free Event ends. 50 discount on PRO features lifetime Fixed bug where purchase history was not restored. If you have a previous purchase history please click the Restore Purchase button. You can create a new diary from the diary list. Color optimization in dark mode

We apologize for any inconvenience caused by a bug associated with the most recent update. Please try our PRO features for free while we fix the issue. If you find a bug please send an email to hello carddiary.me . Other minor bug fixes.

We apologize for any inconvenience caused by a bug associated with the most recent update. Please try our PRO features for free while we fix the issue. If you find a bug please send an email to hello carddiary.me . Other minor bug fixes.

We apologize for any inconvenience caused by a bug caused by the recent update. You can use PRO features for free while we fix major bugs. For users who have subscribed to PRO the subscription date does not increase. It will be renewed on the original renewal date. This promotion may end without notice.

Fixed a bug where PRO purchases could not be restored. It may not be perfect. Please click the restore purchase button. Fixed a bug where the UI was not visible or looked broken. Fixed a bug that caused the app to close when entering the app with a shortcut. We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused by many bugs after the large scale update. We will recover it as quickly as possible.

Big Update Information UI UX design improvements Change app logo. Font change and size optimization. Some changes to the month card design. If the month card is January or December the year can be changed through gestures. Dark mode color change. Changed the date format to suit the language. Improved PDF design. Feature additions changes Added a function that automatically moves faces from thumbnails so that they are not cut off. Changed to view the entire diary by swiping left and right on the Added 24 hour display function. A vibration function has been added to some buttons for accurate recognition. Changed so that notification messages can be written directly. Added a function to temporarily unlock through biometrics when a password is lost. Expansion of available years. 1960 2030 bug fix Fixed a bug that prevented the app from running. Fixed a bug where the basic color of the month card did not change. Fixed a bug where dark mode was not applied when the app was closed. Fixed various bugs that occur during tag creation modification . Fixed a bug where weather information was not displayed. iOS16 or later Fixed a bug that caused the app to close when emptying the trash. Fixed a bug that does not sync between devices. optimization Improved app usage speed. Optimized large iCloud backup and synchronization. etc Stop importing diaries from other apps. We will update again with better features. An unknown bug occurred If you find any bugs please report them. We will fix it quickly. Email: hello carddiary.me

Bug Fix: iOS 11.3 users open Pro features page crash Bug Fix: iPhone SE 5s users UI not show properly v7.0 Card Diary v7.0 is here Yayyy!!! We hope you will enjoy our brand new version We wouldn t call it Card Diary 2 but it s a whole new design and brings lots of wonderful new features. We added a new tab called Mine tab it manage all your diaries photos videos gallery tags locations and settings. Yes We bring TAG LOCATION features in this version. THANKS DRINKS has been removed and PRO features has turned on. We added 1 MONTH 1 YEAR auto subscriptions for our PRO features as well as LIFETIME for the one time purchase to get all PRO features forever. The reason for that is we want to provide a better service to you all and also it will deeply help our continuous development and design work. But still you can use FREE version as long as you want you will get most of our features in FREE version include TAG LOCATION up to 3 each. We do hope you subscribe our PRO features to support our work. We d be very appreciate if you do so. Thanks for loving Card Diary. Optimize: Add Time Zone

We fix a bug that month cards may not show correctly in some devices. Here is the culprit static func yearFirstDayAndLastDay year: Int Date Date let dateFormatter DateFormatter dateFormatter.dateFormat yyyy MM dd HH:mm:ss let firstDayOfTheYear dateFormatter.date from: year 01 01 00:00:00 Date let lastDayOfTheYear dateFormatter.date from: year 12 31 23:59:59 Date return firstDayOfTheYear lastDayOfTheYear
